´Reuben Allerhand 
Went to St. Stephen's School and often played here. 
We will always remember the love and laughter he 
brought to the lives of his family and friends."÷
”This bench was donated for 
David Llewllyn Thomas. 
An old Edwardian who was born and lived at 
no.1 Royal Cresent. He particularly enjoyed 
sitting in this park in the summer listening 
to the band playing"Ð
ŸDedicated to the memory of
John Dennis Harper
07.11.1934 - 17.05.2013
Those we love don't go away, they walk beside us every day,
Unseen, unheard but still always near,
Still loved, still missed and with us here."Ð
